---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import LabHeader from "../components/lab/LabHeader"
import LabFooter from "../components/lab/LabFooter"
---

<Layout title="Projects" metaDescription="Current and past projects from the Thoughtful AI Tools Lab at Calvin University">
	<main>
    <LabHeader client:only="react" />
    
    <section class="px-8 py-20 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl">
      <div class="container mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-blue-gray-900">Projects</h1>
        
        <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-1 xl:grid-cols-1">
          <!-- Textfocals Project -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-blue-gray-900">
              <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2403.01055" target="_blank" class="hover:text-blue-500 transition-colors">
                Textfocals: AI-Generated Views for Writing Support
              </a>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Team: Jiho Kim, Ray C. Flanagan, Noelle E. Haviland, ZeAi Sun, Souad N. Yakubu, Edom A. Maru, Kenneth C. Arnold
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Status: Published at HAI-GEN Workshop 2024
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-3">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm">HCI</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-800 rounded-full text-sm">NLP</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-orange-100 text-orange-800 rounded-full text-sm">Writing Tools</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              Textfocals is a UI prototype that provides LLM-generated summaries, questions, and advice in a sidebar 
              of a text editor, encouraging reflection and self-driven revision in writing without direct text generation. 
              This approach maintains full authorship while leveraging AI to support the writing process.
            </p>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2403.01055" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 bg-blue-600 text-white text-sm rounded hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
                ðŸ“„ Paper
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- AI for Writers 2024-2025 Senior Project -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-blue-gray-900">
              <a href="/projects/ai-writers-2024-25" class="hover:text-blue-500 transition-colors">
                AI for Writers 2024-2025
              </a>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Students: Jason Chew, Daniel Kim | Advisor: Kenneth C. Arnold
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Completed: May 8, 2025
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-3">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm">HCI</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-800 rounded-full text-sm">NLP</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 rounded-full text-sm">Senior Project</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              A Microsoft Word add-in that generates next-sentence suggestions at varying levels of semantic completeness to enhance 
              the writing process. The tool offers four types of suggestions: thought completion, questions, vocabulary, and rhetorical 
              strategies. Published to the Microsoft Store and tested with 9 participants who found the single-sentence scale contributed 
              to more natural, recursive writing workflows.
            </p>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <a href="/projects/ai-writers-2024-25" class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 bg-blue-600 text-white text-sm rounded hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
                ðŸ“– Read More
              </a>
              <a href="https://app.thoughtful-ai.com/" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 bg-green-600 text-white text-sm rounded hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors">
                ðŸš€ Try the Tool
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Cognitive Engagement Research -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-blue-gray-900">
              Promoting End-to-End Intentionality with LLMs
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Team: Jason Chew, Daniel Kim, Jiho Kim, Ray Flanagan | Lead: Kenneth C. Arnold
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
              Status: Ongoing Research
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-3">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm">HCI</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-800 rounded-full text-sm">Cognitive Science</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-red-100 text-red-800 rounded-full text-sm">Research</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              Research investigating how large language models can be designed to promote intentional, 
              goal-directed thinking and support sustained cognitive effort in complex problem-solving scenarios.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <LabFooter client:only="react" />
  </main>
</Layout>
